object.script:
s=screen m=math igb=input.getBool ign=input.getNumber pgn=property.getNumber dl=s.drawLine drf=s.drawRectF dtf=s.drawTriangleF sc=s.setColor dtb=s.drawTextBox dt=s.drawText sf=string.format a1,a2,a3 = {},{},{} startup = 60 timer = 0 dist = 0
ticks = 0
function onTick() rpsMax = pgn("Max RPS") fuelMax = pgn("Max fuel")
speed = m.abs(ign(1))*3.6 rps = ign(2)/rpsMax fuel = ign(3)/fuelMax batt = ign(4) temp = ign(5)
on = igb(1) brake = igb(2) left = igb(3) right = igb(4) low = igb(5) high = igb(6)
heat = temp > 100
if on then timer = m.min(timer+1,startup) dist = dist+(speed/3.6)/60000 if timer >= startup then for i = 1,13 do a1[i] = rps-i*rpsMax/13 >= 0 a2[i] = fuel-(i-1)*fuelMax/5 >= 0 a3[i] = batt-(i-1)/5 >= 0 end else for i = 1,13 do a1[i],a2[i],a3[i] = true,true,true end brake,heat,left,right,low,high = true,true,true,true,true,true end else timer = 0 speed = 0 temp = 0 rps = 0 fuel = 0 batt = 0 brake,heat,left,right,low,high = false,false,false,false,false,false for i = 1,13 do a1[i],a2[i],a3[i] = false,false,false end end end
function onDraw() sgw = s.getWidth()
if sgw > 32 then
sc(150,150,150) --speed dtb(40,6,17,7,m.floor(speed),0,0)
dl(1,7,20,7) dl(20,8,29,17) dl(19,8,28,17)
dl(2,29,18,29) dl(17,28,27,18) dl(18,28,28,18)
dl(67,16,77,6) dl(68,16,78,6) dl(78,7,95,7)
dl(68,19,79,30) dl(69,19,80,30) dl(80,29,94,29)
sc(75,75,75) --shadow
dl(2,8,19,8) dl(19,9,27,17) dl(1,30,18,30) dl(18,29,29,18) dl(69,16,78,7) dl(78,8,94,8) dl(67,19,79,31) dl(79,30,95,30)
if left then sc(0,150,0) else sc(5,5,5) end for i=0,2 do dl(3+i,3,6+i,0) dl(4+i,4,6+i,6) end
if right then sc(0,150,0) else sc(5,5,5) end for i=0,2 do dl(90+i,3,87+i,0) dl(89+i,4,87+i,6) end
if brake then sc(150,0,0) else sc(5,5,5) end dl(12,1,13,1) dl(11,2,11,5) dl(12,5,13,5) dl(16,1,17,1) dl(17,2,17,5) dl(16,5,17,5) dl(14,1,14,4) dl(14,5,15,5)
if heat then sc(150,0,0) else sc(5,5,5) end dl(79,1,80,1) dl(78,2,78,5) dl(79,5,80,5) dl(83,1,84,1) dl(84,2,84,5) dl(83,5,84,5) dl(80,2,80,5) dl(82,2,82,5) dl(81,3,82,3)
for i=0,3 do --speed local c = m.max(speed-i*50,5) sc(c/3,c/3,c) dl(28+i*3,29-i*3,68-i*3,29-i*3) end
for i=0,11 do local c = 150 - i^(1/2)*44 sc(c/3,c/3,c) dl(21+i,31-i,23+i,31-i) dl(73-i,31-i,75-i,31-i) end
sc(5,5,5) --raft rps for i = 1,20 do dl(1+i,25-m.min(i,6),3+i,25-m.min(i,6)) end
for i = 1,20 do --raft temp dl(1+i,10+m.min(i,6),3+i,10+m.min(i,6)) end
for i = 1,20 do --raft batt dl(72+i,16-m.max(i-15,0),74+i,16-m.max(i-15,0)) end
for i = 1,20 do --raft fuel dl(72+i,19+m.max(i-15,0),74+i,19+m.max(i-15,0)) end
sc(50,50,150) --rps for i = 1,m.min(20,m.floor(rps*20)) do dl(1+i,25-m.min(i,6),3+i,25-m.min(i,6)) end
for i = 1,m.min(20,m.floor(temp/100*20)) do -- temp dl(1+i,10+m.min(i,6),3+i,10+m.min(i,6)) end
for i = 1,m.min(20,m.floor(batt*20)) do --batt dl(72+i,16-m.max(i-15,0),74+i,16-m.max(i-15,0)) end
for i = 1,m.min(20,m.floor(fuel*20)) do --fuel dl(72+i,19+m.max(i-15,0),74+i,19+m.max(i-15,0)) end
sc(50,50,50) dt(10,21,sf("%.0f",rps*rpsMax))
dl(11,10,11,13) dl(10,11,13,11) dl(12,13,13,13) dl(14,10,15,10)
dl(80,10,80,13) dl(79,11,82,11) dl(81,13,84,10) dl(83,13,86,13)
s.drawRect(79,22,4,3) dl(80,24,83,24) dl(84,25,85,25) dl(84,23,86,23) dl(85,24,86,24) end
end

s = self
min = 0 max = 1
mean = 0 tick = 1 tickmax = 10 ratios = {}
for i = 1,tickmax do ratios[i] = 0 end
function clamp(x,y,z) return math.min(math.max(x,y),z) end
function pid(p,i,d) return{p=p, i=i, d=d, error=0, diff=0, integral=0, run=function(s, sp, pv, min, max, maxI) local error,diff,out error = sp-pv diff = error-s.error out = error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d s.error = error s.diff = diff if out > min and out < max then s.integral = clamp(s.integral + error*s.i, min, maxI) end return clamp(error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d, min, max) end } end
pid1 = pid(0.02,0.004,0) pid2 = pid(0.1,0.004,0) pid3 = pid(0.3,0.002,0)
function onTick()
air = input.getNumber(1) fuel = input.getNumber(2) target = input.getNumber(4) rps = input.getNumber(5)
on = input.getBool(1)
afr = property.getNumber("Modular engine Air-to-Fuel ratio") boost = property.getNumber("Reduce if RPS overshoots")*0.1 premade = property.getBool("Engine type")
if on and rps > 2 then if premade then out = pid3:run(target, rps, min, max, boost) mult = 1 else if fuel > 0 then ratios[tick] = air/fuel else ratios[tick] = 0 end
tick = tick+1 if tick > tickmax then tick = 1 end
mean = 0 for i,ratio in ipairs(ratios) do mean = mean+ratio end mean = mean/tickmax
if mean > 0 then multdiff = pid1:run(afr, mean, -0.48, 0.05, 0.05) else multdiff = 0 end
out = pid2:run(target, rps, min, max, boost)
mult = 0.52-multdiff end else out = 0 mult = 0 tick = 1 end
output.setNumber(1, out*mult) output.setNumber(2, out)
end

object.script:
m=math pi=m.pi tau=pi*2
function mapPos(horizontalAngle,verticalAngle,horizontalFov,verticalFov) x = w/2 + w/2 * (math.tan(horizontalAngle)/math.tan(horizontalFov)) y = h/2 + h/2 * (math.tan(verticalAngle)/math.tan(verticalFov)) return x,y end
m=math
function onTick() sRawZoom=input.getNumber(8) zoom=sRawZoom/2+.5 compass = (-input.getNumber(1)*360)%360 tc=m.floor(compass+0.5) if tc==0 then tc=360 end rc = -compass*(pi/180) fov = (63-zoom*62.5) vfov=m.rad(fov) --hfov=m.rad(fov*(3/2)) -- for 3x2 hfov=vfov -- for 2x2 ammo=m.floor(input.getNumber(3)) range=input.getNumber(4) sAz=input.getNumber(5) sEl=input.getNumber(6) sAdj=input.getNumber(7) adj=(sAdj/32)*360 rf=input.getBool(5) if range==4000 or range<=0 or range==2000 then range=0 end raz=input.getNumber(2) rel=input.getNumber(3) rdist=input.getNumber(9) end
function onDraw() s=screen w,h=64,64 w2,h2=w/2,h/2 for i=1,8 do s.setColor(255,128,0) if i==8 then s.setColor(255,0,0) elseif i%2==0 then s.setColor(255,255,255) end s.drawLine(5*1.6+2+m.sin(i*pi/4+rc)*8,h-7-m.cos(i*pi/4+rc)*6,5*1.6+2+m.sin(i*pi/4+rc)*6,h-7-m.cos(i*pi/4+rc)*4) end s.setColor(255,128,0)
x,y=mapPos(m.rad(0.125),m.rad(adj-0.125),hfov,vfov) if rf and range>1 then s.drawText(x-3,y-6,string.format("%4im",m.floor(range+0.5))) elseif rf then s.drawText(x+4,y-6,"L") end s.drawRect(2-1,h-21,5*3+2,6) s.drawText(2+1,h-20,string.format("%03i",tc)) --s.drawText(w-16,h-7,string.format("%3i",ammo)) s.setColor(255,255,255,200) if fov<18 then for i=-10,10,1 do sz=0.5 if i%2==0 then sz=1 end x1,y1=mapPos(m.rad(-sz),m.rad(i+adj),hfov,vfov) x2,y2=mapPos(m.rad(0),m.rad(i+adj),hfov,vfov) s.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end for i=-10,10,1 do sz=0.5 if i%2==0 then sz=1 end x1,y1=mapPos(m.rad(i),m.rad(sz+adj),hfov,vfov) x2,y2=mapPos(m.rad(i),m.rad(adj),hfov,vfov) s.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end else x1,y1=mapPos(0,m.rad(adj-10),hfov,vfov) x2,y2=mapPos(0,m.rad(10+adj),hfov,vfov) s.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) x1,y1=mapPos(m.rad(-10),m.rad(adj),hfov,vfov) x2,y2=mapPos(m.rad(10),m.rad(adj),hfov,vfov) s.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end s.setColor(255,128,0) if rdist>10 then RadarX,RadarY=mapPos(raz*tau,-rel*tau,hfov,vfov) if raz~=0 and rel~=0 then s.drawCircle(RadarX,RadarY,3) if RadarX<4 or RadarX>w-4 or RadarY<4 or RadarY>h-4 then s.drawLine(RadarX,RadarY,w/2,h/2) end end end end

object.script:
m=math pi=m.pi tau=pi*2 sin=m.sin cos=m.cos tan=m.tan atan=m.atan s=screen gn=input.getNumber gb=input.getBool sx,sy,sz=0,0,0 flash=0 handoff=false data=false lock=false massdata=false emergency=false timeout=0 w,h=63,63 grace=property.getNumber("Lock grace period (ticks)") or 20 forceshoot=false emtick=0
function onTick() tx,ty,tz,tm=gn(5),gn(6),gn(7),m.floor(gn(8)+.5) -- transmit rx,ry,rz,rm=gn(9),gn(10),gn(11),m.floor(gn(15)+.5) -- receive mx,my,mz=gn(12),gn(13),gn(14) -- my radioslave=gb(6) and gb(2) cihdg=gn(16) cirange=gn(17) cimass=gn(18)
sane=(rx~=0 and ry~=0) and radioslave -- if datalink is sane
set_eme=cirange>1 and cirange<4999 and radioslave and cimass~=0 if set_eme then emtick=120 sx,sy,sz,sm=rx,ry,rz,rm end emergency=emtick>0 if emtick==1 then handoff=false massdata=false data=false sm=0 end if emergency then emtick=emtick-1 end forceshoot=false
lock = (gb(4) or lock) and not gb(3) and gb(2)
if gb(4) and gb(2) then sm=tm elseif gb(3) then sx,sy,sz,sm=0,0,0,0 end
if sane and not lock then sx,sy,sz=rx,ry,rz massdata=rm~=400 and rm>10 if massdata then sm=rm end if flash==0 then data=true handoff=false flash=60 end end
if emergency and cimass~=0 then massdata=true data=true sm=cimass end
nearby=m.sqrt((tx-rx)^2+(ty-ry)^2+(tz-rz)^2) < 100 and rx~=0 and ry~=0 if massdata and radioslave then if sm==tm and not lock then lock=true flash=60 handoff=true data=false timeout=grace end elseif radioslave then if nearby and not lock then sm=tm lock=true flash=60 handoff=true data=false timeout=grace end end
if sm==tm then timeout=grace sx,sy,sz=tx,ty,tz end
lock=lock and timeout~=0 and sm~=0
ox,oy,oz=sx-mx,sy-my,sz-mz
if sx~=0 and sy~=0 then range=m.sqrt(ox^2+oy^2+oz^2) heading=m.deg(atan(ox,oy)) elevation=m.deg(atan(oz,m.sqrt(ox^2+oy^2))) else range=0 heading=-800 elevation=-800 end
if emergency and not lock and (rx==0 and ry==0 and rz==0) then heading=cihdg elevation=10 elseif emergency and sm==tm then forceshoot=true end
flash=m.max(flash-1,0) timeout=m.max(timeout-1,0)
output.setBool(1,(lock or radioslave) and ((sx~=0 and sy~=0) or emergency)) output.setBool(3,lock)
output.setBool(30,forceshoot)
output.setNumber(1,heading%360) output.setNumber(2,elevation) end
minrng=100 maxrng=3100
dy=8 size=30
function onDraw() w,h=63,63 s.setColor(255,128,0) if range>100 and sx~=0 and sy~=0 then s.drawTextBox(1,1,w,h,string.format("%0.2fkm",range/1000),-1,-1) end if radioslave then s.drawTextBox(1,1,w-2,h,"SLAVE",1,-1) end if flash%10>4 then if handoff then s.drawTextBox(4,10,w,h,"*HANDOFF*",0,0) elseif data then s.drawTextBox(4,10,w,h,"*DATA*",0,0) end end if lock then if timeout==grace-1 then s.drawTextBox(4,20,w,h,"*LOCK*",0,0) else s.drawTextBox(4,20,w,h,"LOCK",0,0) end end if emergency then s.drawTextBox(4,30,w,h,"COUNTER",0,0) end if sx~=0 and sy~=0 then drange1 = m.sqrt((sx-mx)^2+(sy-my)^2+(sz-mz)^2) else drange1 = 0 end local drawy = 30-(drange1/5000)*30 s.drawLine(1,dy,1,dy+size) for i=0,5000,500 do local drange = i local drawy = size-(drange/5000)*size if i%1000==0 then drawx=5 else drawx=3 end s.drawLine(1,dy+drawy,drawx,dy+drawy) end s.setColor(0,50,100,200) local drawyl,drawyu = size-(minrng/5000)*size+1,size-(maxrng/5000)*size+1 s.drawTriangleF(1,dy+drawyl,5,dy+drawyl,5,dy-4+drawyl) s.drawTriangleF(1,dy+drawyu,5,dy+drawyu,5,dy+4+drawyu) if range>minrng and range<maxrng then s.setColor(5,255,10,200) else s.setColor(50,0,100,200) end if drange1~=0 then local drawy = math.floor(30-(drange1/5000)*30+.5) s.drawLine(2,dy+drawy,5,dy+drawy+3) s.drawLine(2,dy+drawy,5,dy+drawy-3) end end

object.script:
azi=0 ele=0 function onTick() slave=input.getBool(1) on=input.getBool(2)
idleE=input.getNumber(10)*360
zoom=(0.5+input.getNumber(4)/2) fov = (63-zoom*62.5)
zMult=zoom+0.1
az=input.getNumber(1) azi=(azi+(az/60)*fov+540)%360-180
el=input.getNumber(2) ele=ele+(el/60)*fov
hdg=(input.getNumber(5)*-360+360)%360 idle=(input.getNumber(6)*-360+360)%360
goHdg=input.getNumber(7) goEle=input.getNumber(8)
if slave and goHdg~=-800 and goEle~=-800 then azi=goHdg ele=goEle end
if ele>80 then ele=80 elseif ele>idleE+80 then ele=idleE+80 elseif ele<idleE then ele=idleE end
if on then output.setNumber(1,azi) output.setNumber(2,ele) else output.setNumber(1,idle) output.setNumber(2,0) azi=hdg ele=0 end end

m=math pi=m.pi tau=pi*2 sin=m.sin cos=m.cos print=print or function() end
function bankAngle(tiltside,pitch,tiltup) b = math.asin(math.sin(tiltside))/math.sin(pi*.5-(pitch)) if tiltup<0 then b = pi-b end return (b+pi)%tau-pi end
IdentVector={1,1,1,1}
IdentMatrix={ {1,0,0,0},--x {0,1,0,0},--y {0,0,1,0},--z {0,0,0,1}}--w
out={0,0,0,0}

object.script:
-- EPN with fallback guidance law by Lassi#9944
-- Navigation constants NY = property.getText("Yaw navigation constant") or 5 NP = property.getText("Pitch navigation constant") or 7
-- [NEW] Defining mathematical functions m=math tau=m.pi*2 pi=tau/2 atan=m.atan sqrt=m.sqrt
-- Defining global vars ldyaw = 0 ldpitch = 0 ldistance = 0 lloshr = 0 llosvr = 0 llosha = 0 llosva = 0 x, y, z = 0, 0, 0 tx, ty, tz = 0, 0, 0 lx, ly, lz = 0, 0, 0 dx, dy, dz = 0, 0, 0 closingv = 0 loshr = 0 losvr = 0 losha = 0 losva = 0 loshj = 0 losvj = 0 distance = 0 runtime = 0 fuzed = false finYaw = 0 finPitch = 0 tgo = 75 lspeed = 0 lastX = 0 lastY = 0 lastZ = 0 accel = 0 speed = 0 dmX = 0 dmY = 0 dmZ = 0 speedPeak=0 accelPeak=0
function clamp(x,min,max) return math.min(math.max(x,min),max) end
function onTick() rx = input.getNumber(1) ry = input.getNumber(2) rz = input.getNumber(3) launch = input.getNumber(7)>0
accept = rx ~= 0 and ry ~= 0 if accept then if input.getNumber(9)>0 then -- Fine mode (compensates for tick delay, not guaranteed to work with inaccuracy of SARH) tx, ty, tz = rx, ry, rz dtx, dty, dtz = tx - lx, ty-ly, tz-lz x, y, z = tx+dtx*2, ty+dty*2, tz+dtz*2 else -- Normal mode x, y, z = rx, ry, rz end end
X = input.getNumber(4) Y = input.getNumber(5) Z = input.getNumber(6)
-- LOS vector dx = x - X dy = y - Y dz = z - Z
-- Magnitude of LOS vector distance = sqrt(dx ^ 2 + dy ^ 2 + dz ^ 2)
-- Direction of LOS vector dyaw = atan(dx,dy) dpitch = atan(dz,sqrt(dx ^ 2 + dy ^ 2))
dmX = (X - lastX)*60 dmY = (Y - lastY)*60 dmZ = (Z - lastZ)*60
selfCrs = atan(dmX,dmY) selfVV = atan(dmZ,sqrt(dmX^2+dmY^2))
speed = sqrt(dmX ^ 2 + dmY ^ 2 + dmZ ^ 2) accel = (speed - lspeed) * 60
pursuitX = (dyaw-selfCrs+pi)%tau-pi pursuitY = dpitch-selfVV
-- Guidance variables if accept then closingv = (ldistance - distance) * 60 loshr = dyaw - ldyaw losvr = dpitch - ldpitch losha = (loshr - lloshr) losva = (losvr - llosvr) loshj = (losha - llosha) losvj = (losva - llosva) tgo = distance / closingv finYaw = loshr * math.abs(closingv) + loshj*tgo *5 + losha*tgo^2 finPitch = losvr * math.abs(closingv) + losvj*tgo *5 + losva*tgo^2 end
output.setBool(1,false)
if launch and not fuzed then -- Guidance control output.setNumber(2,(0.02+0.02*(speed/150))) -- Trim if no lock output.setNumber(1,-0) if x ~= 0 and y ~= 0 and closingv>20 and distance<3000 then output.setNumber(2,-finPitch * NP * clamp(tgo/6,0.3,1) * clamp(1-tgo/8,0.75,1) + 0.02 + 0.02*(speed/150)) output.setNumber(1,-(finYaw * NY * clamp(tgo/6,0.3,1) * clamp(1-tgo/8,0.75,1))) elseif x ~= 0 and y ~= 0 then -- fallback pure pursuit output.setNumber(2,-pursuitY + 0.02 + 0.02*(speed/150)) output.setNumber(1,-pursuitX) end
-- Debug runtime = runtime + 1 output.setNumber(3,runtime)
-- Fuze if (((distance < 35 and tgo < 0.177) or (distance < 100 and accel < -50)) and x ~= 0 and y ~= 0 and z ~= 0 and runtime>30) or runtime>2400 then output.setBool(1,true) end fuzed = fuzed or input.getNumber(8)>0
speedPeak=math.max(speedPeak,speed) accelPeak=math.max(accelPeak,accel) end
-- Last variables ldyaw = dyaw ldpitch = dpitch ldistance = distance lloshr = loshr llosvr = losvr llosha = losha llosva = losva lastX = X lastY = Y lastZ = Z lspeed = speed
output.setNumber(4,x) output.setNumber(5,y) output.setNumber(6,z) output.setNumber(7,X) output.setNumber(8,Y) output.setNumber(9,Z) output.setNumber(10,speed) output.setNumber(11,speedPeak) output.setNumber(12,accel) output.setNumber(13,accelPeak)
output.setBool(2,x==0 and y==0) output.setBool(3,X==0 and Y==0) output.setBool(4,accept) output.setBool(5,fuzed) output.setBool(6,launch)
if accept then lx = tx ly = ty lz = tz end end
